narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I decline to answer this question.
A fellow history student does not have a choice in the matter, so yes, I would recommend taking this course if you would like to graduate.
